      "id": "sybil_24_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_24",
      "description": "This collector-grade E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance. Power is derived from the S54 3.2L straight-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual and an M-variable differential lock. This example is mechanically flawless: the subframe has been inspected and reinforced, rod bearings have been addressed as preventative maintenance, and the suspension geometry remains tight with fresh OEM bushings. Finished in concours-level paint with a pristine interior, this is a turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
